default"The dialogue process allows different perspectives to come in.  For government also risk management as well involved. If people disagree it is a good way to say we have taken into account public opinion. ... It was very useful when we were questioned by sceptics 
defaultabout why the research was licensed and we could refer back – robust evidence base – and say these are the findings.  We had followed a robust process and this couldn’t be questioned."
